OL,3,CMan charged over fatal dual
OL,4,Ccarriageway crash
OL,6,FA man has been charged in connection
OL,7,Fwith a fatal crash on the A19 in
OL,8,FSunderland.
OL,10,FKane Farragher, 24, of Birkenhead, has
OL,11,Fbeen charged with causing death by
OL,12,Fdangerous driving, causing death by
OL,13,Fdriving whilst disqualified, and cause
OL,14,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,16,FHe is due to appear before South
OL,17,FTyneside Magistrates' Court on Tuesday
OL,18,F(3 March).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
