OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772572329
OL,3,CMan charged over fatal dual
OL,4,Ccarriageway crash
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police previously said a
OL,7,Fcollision took place in Sunderland at
OL,8,Faround 3am on Sunday (1 March)
OL,9,Finvolving a grey Volkswagen Sharan and
OL,10,Fa white BMW.
OL,12,FA woman in her 20s, who was a
OL,13,Fpassenger in the BMW, died at the
OL,14,Fscene, the force said.
OL,16,FA male passenger of the BMW, aged in
OL,17,Fhis 20s, suffered serious injuries and
OL,18,Fremains in hospital in a life-
OL,19,Fthreatening condition.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
