OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772572329
OL,3,CMan charged over fatal dual
OL,4,Ccarriageway crash
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Northumbria Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Members of the public are asked
OL,8,Fnot to speculate ` either online or in
OL,9,Fthe community ` and respect the
OL,10,Fongoing legal proceedings."
OL,12,FAnyone with information or footage
OL,13,Fshould contact the force.
